reviewText:
This DVD is imported from Holland, but it is designed to be playable worldwide.

Here are the correct specs:

Region Coding: 0 (ALL Regions)
Video Format: NTSC
Audio Formats: Dolby 2.0, Dolby 5.1, and DTS 5.1

The concert video itself is a killer representation of the band during the Paich-less years with Kimball on lead vocals.
